        "suggestion": "Move to a structured error policy: expose a constant outward message (no raw `%v`), keep full cause in `cause` only, and add explicit classifier-based redaction where needed; codify contract tests to assert forbidden substrings from representative upstream errors while keeping `errors.Is/Unwrap` behavior.",
