        "related_files": [
          "goseg/importer/importer.go",
          "goseg/shipworkflow/lifecycle.go",
          "goseg/handler/support.go"
        ],
        "evidence": [
          "`configureUploadedPier` in `goseg/importer/importer.go` combines request validation, phase selection, upload extraction, system config reads/mutation, network/wireguard scheduling, transition operations, and cleanup dispatch.",
          "The function also relies on explicit asynchronous task spawning (`go` calls) and transition publishing inline, mixing domain orchestration with external side-effect control rather than delegating to dedicated workflow components."
        ],
        "suggestion": "Refactor importer flow into a pipeline: parse/validate input, delegate extraction to a dedicated extractor stage, delegate state transitions to workflow coordinator, and keep side-effect scheduling/cleanup in dedicated services with explicit interfaces.",
        "reasoning": ""
      },
      "status": "auto_resolved",
      "note": "Disappeared from scan \u2014 likely fixed",
