      "detector": "review",
      "file": ".",
      "tier": 3,
      "confidence": "high",
      "summary": "Filesystem cleanup in Hoon file helpers swallows failure states",
      "detail": {
        "holistic": true,
        "dimension": "error_consistency",
        "related_files": [
          "goseg/click/hoon.go",
          "goseg/click/internal/runtime/runtime.go",
          "goseg/click/notify/notify.go"
        ],
        "evidence": [
          "`deleteHoon` ignores `os.Stat` errors other than `os.IsNotExist` and ignores `os.Remove` errors completely (`goseg/click/hoon.go:40-42`).",
          "The same pattern exists in `runtime.DeleteHoon` (`goseg/click/internal/runtime/runtime.go:34-40`), so multiple call chains inherit silent failure behavior."
